#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:53
#, no-c-format
msgid "Using &kimagemapeditor;"
msgstr "&kimagemapeditor; gebruiken"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:55
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kimagemapeditor; is a &HTML; imagemap editor developed by the &kde; "
"community. It allows you to create and modify &HTML; <ulink url=\"http://en."
"wikipedia.org/wiki/Imagemap\">Imagemaps.</ulink>"
msgstr ""
"&kimagemapeditor; is een &HTML; imagemap-editor ontwikkeld door de &kde; "
"gemeenschap. Het stelt u in staat om &HTML;-<ulink url=\"http://en.wikipedia."
"org/wiki/Imagemap\">imagemaps</ulink> aan te maken en te wijzigen."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:61
#, no-c-format
